cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper deals with generating and transforming facial images using GANs, which is a popular topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a novel iterative architecture for GAN training, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of perceptual loss in the proposed model also relates to multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories.
